{"tid":1433102,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（手已分）同毒撚拍拖好辛苦","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:14:49.000Z","uid":302756,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d479c9b930fe3d4bdbfea1877c67d2ac4418d562","tid":1433102,"uid":302756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"大學生第一次拍拖，覺得自己3年幾嘅努力同青春白費哂。我從來都唔識點樣嬲人，通常有咩事都只係識得唔開心，直到爆煲先識發下脾氣。佢經常話忙/攰，我哋呢3年內見面嘅次數不足50次。（只食個飯都包括埋）以前成日諗住佢放大假就會陪我，但我已經再欺騙唔到自己。就算夜晚講電話，好多話題都係佢嘅禁忌唔講得，我覺得我做嘅樣樣嘢都係錯。<br />\n<br />\n我已經同佢講咗分手，但依然唔識用咩心情去應對之後嘅事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dd94e046b139a801c728774701a3df194ac14c","tid":1433102,"uid":254923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"3年見唔夠50次扑左幾次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb9e3f05611313295fd333424887051a7e68b5d","tid":1433102,"uid":191555,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"成件事關毒撚咩事?"},{"pid":"9c057587d4b4adcda095e6b4a8303118f437f6ea","tid":1433102,"uid":66810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"又屈毒撚機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你見過毒撚未"},{"pid":"9643d24681dfe36f64e5591ebf4c7e11ff3d7312","tid":1433102,"uid":302756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2fb9e3f05611313295fd333424887051a7e68b5d","tid":1433102,"uid":191555,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"成件事關毒撚咩事?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:51:26.000Z","msg":"巴打你啱<br />\n啱啱拍拖嗰陣佢話佢自己毒 唔好期望佢會經常同我出街<br />\n一個月都見唔到一次面已經唔係毒可以解釋得到"},{"pid":"6a37314d1706457a6c0c5d110159da6de7c7e61c","tid":1433102,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9643d24681dfe36f64e5591ebf4c7e11ff3d7312","tid":1433102,"uid":302756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2fb9e3f05611313295fd333424887051a7e